property.name: note
property.value:
Param "calm" floats from 0 to 1 based on progress in the feather minigame.
For the "gondola_idle" parameter... I think we floated it along with the calm parameter to dial back the intensity of the gondola shaking idle sfx.
(If you play event:/game/04_cliffside/gondola_halted_loop in another window/tab, you can hear the effects of tweaking this parameter.)
